org.ejbca.core.ejb.audit.enums

Enum EjbcaEventTypes

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<EjbcaEventTypes>
      • org.ejbca.core.ejb.audit.enums.EjbcaEventTypes
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<EjbcaEventTypes>, org.cesecore.audit.enums.ConstantType<org.cesecore.audit.enums.EventType>, org.cesecore.audit.enums.EventType

    public enum EjbcaEventTypes
extends java.lang.Enum<EjbcaEventTypes>
implements org.cesecore.audit.enums.EventType
    EJBCA specific security audit event types, for audit using CESecore's audit log. These event types extend the list of already existing event types of CESeCore.
    See Also:
    EventTypes, EjbcaModuleTypes, EjbcaServiceTypes
